# Branch instruction codes are J-Type format w/ 16 bits for branch address
# This value is word-addressed (0x01 = 1 word, not 1 byte)
# It is also a signed 16-bit integer

# The max distance as an address distance is +/- 2^17 bytes.
# The max distance in number of statements is +/- 2^15 instructions.

